{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1679-06_065", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Sonnet faite par une Dame]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", juin 1679 [tome 6], p. 65-67."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Apres un Sonnet Italien, il faut vous en faire voir un François. Vous le devez lire avec plaisir, puis qu’il est fait par une Personne de vostre Sexe. Les Belles qui ne se piquent pas toûjours de fidelité, trouvent quelquefois des Infidelles. C'est là-dessus que Mademoiselle Moussard s’est divertie à faire ces Vers."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "UN aveugle transport de tout mon sort décide,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "C'est par un Inconstant que mon cœur est charmé ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Et quoy qu’il ait perdu tout espoir d’estre aimé,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Il cede à ce panchant qui l’entraîne & le guide."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[1]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Une Etoille fatale à mon destin préside ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Elle entretient toújours un feu trop allumé,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce funeste desir par l’amour confirmé,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Malgré moy me condamne à chérir un Perfide."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[2]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[2]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "O vous, qui pouvez tout, & versez dans le cœur"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Ou la tendre foiblesse, ou l’austere rigueur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Que vous partagez mal vos froideurs & vos flâmes !"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[3]", "tag": "ab", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/ab[3]/text()[1]", "text": "***"}], "attributes": {"type": "ornament"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Astres trop inhumains qui causez mes soucis,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Que ne me laissiez-vous la plus fiere des Ames,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[17]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[17]/text()[1]", "text": "Ou que ne donniez-vous ma tendresse à Tirsis ?"}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Si un Inconstant a pû donner lieu à ce Sonnet, il y a des fidélitez inviolables, & je puis vous le prouver par Certificat."}]}]}